==荣誉==

影片获得1974年第27届[[英国电影学院奖最佳影片|英国电影学院奖最佳影片]]、最佳导演和最佳女配角奖，以及[[奥斯卡最佳外语片|奥斯卡最佳外语片]]<ref name="Oscars1974">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/46th-winners.html |title=The 46th Academy Awards (1974) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2011-12-03 |work=oscars.org |archive-date=2014-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802064704/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/46th-winners.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。导演获提名[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|奥斯卡最佳导演奖]]，[[Valentina_Cortese|Valentina Cortese]]获提名[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|奥斯卡最佳女配角奖]]。

本片被认为是导演最重要的作品之一，《[[时代周刊|时代周刊]]》将本片和《[[四百击|四百击]]》列入20世纪百大佳片之中<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.time.com/time/2005/100movies/the_complete_list.html | work=Time | title=All-Time 100 Movies | accessdate=2010-05-01 | date=2005-02-12 | archive-date=2007-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070314020006/http://www.time.com/time/2005/100movies/the_complete_list.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

